# Local runtime state: whatever you load into the app stays on your machine.
data/*.db
data/*.db-*
data/*.log

# NOTE: tests/fixtures/*.json and sample/* ARE committed — the test suite and the
# app demo need them. They are generated from a seeded RNG by
# scripts/make_synthetic_fixtures.py and describe invented funds (ZZ ISINs), so
# there is nothing confidential in them. If you point this tool at real holdings,
# that data lives in data/ and is ignored above — keep it that way.
